                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " All measurements were performed using an HPGe",
                "detector with 50% efficiency with respect to NaI and",
                "the FWHM was 1.8 keV for a gamma energy of 1.3 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "3CZRUJF"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " the U-120M cyclotron."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDGT"
                ],
                "institute": "4ZZZDUB"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " EG-5 electrostatic generator. Experiment",
                "was performed to reduce the energy spread of deuterons",
                "in the subbarrier energy region."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The stack of targets consisting of scandium foils with",
                "thicknesses from 3 to 5 um was installed at the center",
                "of the reaction chamber of U-120M, under the deuteron",
                "beam. The stack also included titanium foils with",
                "thicknesses of 1.8 um, which were used for the monitor",
                "reaction. Aluminium degraders with thicknesses from",
                "5 to 50 um were installed between targets to reduce the",
                "deuteron energy. Deuteron energies of 11.7 to 2.0 MeV",
                "were absorbed in the applied arrays of Sc targets.",
                "Scandium foils, thickness, 2 um, were irradiated by a",
                "deuteron beam of EG-5 with an energy varying from",
                "0.9 to 2.5MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
