            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target stack consisted of six Sc foils with",
                "thicknesses of 3 to 5 um. The first stack was",
                "irradiated with a calculated 6He energy of 20 MeV.",
                "A stack of three Sc foils was irradiated by a 6He beam",
                "with an energy of ions incident on the stack of about",
                " 23 MeV.",
                "In both arrays, Al foils with different thicknesses",
                "were placed between the Sc targets to measure the 6He",
                "energy."
